description: Paula Deen sits down each week with family and friends to discuss tips on food and cooking. Want to offer your take or ask a question? She just might give you call...
title: What's Cooking with Paula Deen

episodes.title: Get Crispy Chicken with the Airfryer!
episodes.description: Paula talks to a caller about using the airfryer to make the BEST crispy chicken and explains why airfryers are really a fast, healthy, and always delicious way to make crispy recipes for the family.

episodes.title: Pecan Pie with Homemade Crust
episodes.description: Paula makes a Pecan Pie for her brother with Georgia pecans. The secret to the pie is her amazing homemade pie crust. She hopes you will feel comfortable making your very own pie crust.

episodes.description: Paula discusses the culinary secrets of making pie crust with a caller, plus adding a few tips about incorporating coconut and yogurt...Happy Pie Making!

episodes.title: What's Cooking with Paula Deen - Asparagus Sandwich, Rice Salad and Chocolate Bananas
episodes.description: We are all safer at home right now... So Paula is in the kitchen preparing a nice backyard springtime picnic to share with her friend, Sandy. Paula is making a healthy asparagus sandwich, rice salad, frozen banana covered in chocolate and nuts served with homemade lemonade. Enjoy!

episodes.title: Paula talks about book signings, appearances, and air-fryer love.
